Project: Architect Auth Module
URL: https://architect-testing.projectsmate.com/login
Date: 19 FEB 2026

Scope of Testing
This document covers manual testing of the Login module including:

1. Functional testing

TC_001 – Verify Login Page Loads Successfully       
Test ID : TC_001
Objective : Verify login page loads correctly
Steps : Open login URL
Expected Result : Login page loads without errors

TC_002 – Login with Valid Credentials
Test ID : TC_002
Objective : Verify successful login
Steps : Enter valid email and password → Click Login
Expected Result : User is logged in successfully

TC_003 – Verify Google Sign-in Button
Test ID : TC_003
Objective : Verify Google authentication
Steps : Click "Sign in with Google"
Expected Result : Redirect to Google authentication page

2. Negative testing

TC_004 – Login with Invalid Password
Test ID : TC_004
Objective : Verify error message for wrong password
Steps : Enter valid email + invalid password → Click Login
Expected Result : Proper error message displayed

TC_005 – Login with Invalid Email Format
Test ID : TC_005
Objective : Validate email format
Steps : Enter invalid email (abc@) → Click Login
Expected Result : Email validation error shown

TC_006 – Empty Email Field
Test ID : TC_006
Objective : Verify required field validation
Steps : Leave email empty → Click Login
Expected Result : Required field message displayed

TC_007 – Both Fields Empty
Test ID : TC_007
Objective : Verify form submission blocked
Steps : Leave both fields empty → Click Login
Expected Result : Validation messages shown

3. Observations
No visible Sign Up option found on login page.
Login page contains Google sign-in option.
Form validation behavior observed during testing.


  